          <div style="display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;font-size:13px;color:var(--text2);line-height:1.7;">
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;">1️⃣</span>
              <div><strong style="color:var(--text);">Select your microphone</strong> from the dropdown. Click "Refresh Mics" if your device isn't listed. Grant browser permission when prompted.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;">2️⃣</span>
              <div><strong style="color:var(--text);">Enter a title and speaker name.</strong> These appear on the listener player in real time.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;">3️⃣</span>
              <div><strong style="color:var(--text);">Click GO LIVE.</strong> Your microphone audio streams instantly to all listeners — no external app needed.</div>
            </div>
            <div style="display:flex;gap:12px;align-items:flex-start;">
              <span style="font-size:20px;flex-shrink:0;">4️⃣</span>
              <div><strong style="color:var(--text);">Stop to return to scheduled playback.</strong> The listener player switches sources automatically.</div>
