            <div style="padding:12px;background:rgba(212,168,67,0.06);border:1px solid rgba(212,168,67,0.2);border-radius:8px;font-size:12px;">
              <strong style="color:var(--gold);">💡 Tip:</strong> Use a headset or external microphone for best quality. Use <strong>Monitor</strong> to hear yourself before going live.
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Sound-check panel (pre-broadcast mic test) -->
